name: Realistic Socks - Sexy Legs and Feet (NSFW)
description:
Let's celebrate beautiful socks!

Download this model and activate it with a strength of 0.3-0.7 (I use 0.6). No arbitrary keywords needed, but make sure you mention socks otherwise the feet might be cut off in the image.

This LoRa is great for adding socks to a variety of poses. HOWEVER, it's not the greatest at handling soles. I made a LoRa specifically for that purpose, here: https://civitai.com/models/26357/realistic-socks-soles-sexy-legs-and-feet-nsfw

Usage:

Avoid the word "feet" since it skews the AI towards rendering toes, which often ruin the soft sock details.

Example Prompts + Notes:

General Purpose: "Woman wearing socks, legs spread"

Very high quality, but often just feet: "legs, pink socks"

Use the "legs spread" pose for fairly strong results: "legs spread, blue striped socks"

Try your own pose descriptions, but make sure you mention 'socks' in the prompt - it helps to emphasize with (): "(yellow socks), woman, sexy, [[Your chosen pose]]"
